{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882667339,"sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","part":{"id":"prt_d7adafe7d001guKIg2tojBgW4Q","messageID":"msg_d7adae6ab001LwaaubpTbs2w1t","sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ab99d7455d5a4c589a465ace9edd29fd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Specification: AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端\n2: \n3: **Module:** sdk-python  \n4: **Language:** Python  \n5: **Size:** M\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: 为 AgentCube Python SDK 实现统一的 HTTP 客户端基础设施，支持控制面和数据面的 HTTP 通信，包括连接池管理、超时配置、会话管理和错误处理。\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Requirements\n16: \n17: ### Requirement: HTTP Session 创建与连接池\n18: \n19: 系统应使用 `requests.Session` 配合 `HTTPAdapter` 实现连接池复用，支持自定义连接池大小。\n20: \n21: #### Scenario: 默认连接池配置\n22: \n23: - **GIVEN** 调用 `create_session()` 不传入参数\n24: - **WHEN** 创建 HTTP session\n25: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 为 `http://` 和 `https://` 两个 scheme 各挂载一个 `HTTPAdapter`，连接池参数为 `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: 自定义连接池配置\n28: \n29: - **GIVEN** 调用 `create_session(pool_connections=20, pool_maxsize=30)`\n30: - **WHEN** 创建 HTTP session\n31: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 使用指定的参数创建 `HTTPAdapter` 并挂载到两个 scheme\n32: \n33: #### Scenario: Session 返回类型\n34: \n35: - **GIVEN** `create_session()` 被调用\n36: - **WHEN** 函数返回\n37: - **THEN** 返回值 SHALL 是 `requests.Session` 实例\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ### Requirement: Control Plane HTTP 客户端\n42: \n43: 系统应实现 `ControlPlaneClient` 支持 Workload Manager 的会话管理 API。\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: 创建会话请求\n46: \n47: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` 实例已初始化，且有有效的 `auth_token`\n48: - **WHEN** 调用 `create_session(name=\"test\", namespace=\"default\", ttl=3600)`\n49: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 发送 `POST {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` 请求，包含：\n50:   - Header `Content-Type: application/json`\n51:   - Header `Authorization: Bearer {token}`\n52:   - JSON body `{\"name\": \"test\", \"namespace\": \"default\", \"ttl\": 3600, \"metadata\": null}`\n53:   - 超时 `(connect_timeout, timeout)` 默认 `(5.0, 120)`\n54: - **AND** 返回响应中的 `data[\"sessionId\"]`\n55: - **AND** 若响应缺少 `sessionId` 则抛出 `ValueError`\n56: \n57: #### Scenario: 创建会话带 metadata\n58: \n59: - **GIVEN** 调用 `create_session(name=\"test\", namespace=\"default\", metadata={\"key\": \"value\"}, ttl=3600)`\n60: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n61: - **THEN** JSON body SHALL 包含 `metadata: {\"key\": \"value\"}`\n62: \n63: #### Scenario: 删除会话 - 成功\n64: \n65: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 存在且有效\n66: - **WHEN** 调用 `delete_session(session_id)`\n67: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 发送 `DELETE {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}`\n68: - **AND** 返回 `True`\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: 删除会话 - 404 视为成功\n71: \n72: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 不存在\n73: - **WHEN** 服务端返回 404\n74: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 返回 `True`（而非抛出异常）\n75: \n76: #### Scenario: 删除会话 - 其他错误\n77: \n78: - **GIVEN** 服务端返回非 2xx/404 错误\n79: - **WHEN** `delete_session` 执行\n80: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 记录警告日志\n81: - **AND** 返回 `False`\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Workload Manager URL 解析\n84: \n85: - **GIVEN** 构造函数未传入 `workload_manager_url`\n86: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n87: - **THEN** `base_url` SHALL 从环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 获取\n88: \n89: #### Scenario: Workload Manager URL 显式传入\n90: \n91: - **GIVEN** 构造函数传入 `workload_manager_url=\"https://wm.example.com\"`\n92: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n93: - **THEN** `base_url` SHALL 使用传入的值\n94: \n95: #### Scenario: Auth Token 解析 - 参数优先\n96: \n97: - **GIVEN** 构造函数传入 `auth_token=\"my-token\"`\n98: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n99: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 使用传入的 token，设置默认 header `Authorization: Bearer my-token`\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: Auth Token 解析 - 从文件读取\n102: \n103: - **GIVEN** 构造函数未传入 `auth_token`\n104: - **AND** 文件 `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 存在且包含 `sa-token`\n105: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n106: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 调用 `read_token_from_file` 读取 token\n107: - **AND** 设置默认 header `Authorization: Bearer sa-token`\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: Auth Token 为空 - 无 Authorization header\n110: \n111: - **GIVEN** 构造函数未传入 `auth_token`\n112: - **AND** token 文件不存在或为空\n113: - **WHEN** 初始化 `ControlPlaneClient`\n114: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL NOT 设置 `Authorization` header\n115: \n116: #### Scenario: Close 方法\n117: \n118: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` 有活跃的 HTTP session\n119: - **WHEN** 调用 `client.close()`\n120: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 关闭底层的 `requests.Session`\n121: \n122: ---\n123: \n124: ### Requirement: Code Interpreter Data Plane HTTP 客户端\n125: \n126: 系统应实现 `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 支持 Router 代理的代码执行和文件操作 API。\n127: \n128: #### Scenario: Base URL 构建 - 从参数\n129: \n130: - **GIVEN** 构造时传入 `base_url=\"https://router.example.com/path/\"`\n131: - **WHEN** 初始化客户端\n132: - **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL 直接使用传入的 `base_url`\n133: \n134: #### Scenario: Base URL 构建 - 从 router_url 和 cr_name\n135: \n136: - **GIVEN** 构造时传入 `router_url=\"https://router.example.com\"`, `namespace=\"prod\"`, `cr_name=\"my-interpreter\"`\n137: - **AND** 未传入 `base_url`\n138: - **WHEN** 初始化客户端\n139: - **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL 为 `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/prod/code-interpreters/my-interpreter/invocations/\")`\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: 会话头设置\n142: \n143: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 已初始化，`session_id` 为 `\"abc123\"`\n144: - **WHEN** 发送任意 HTTP 请求\n145: - **THEN** 请求 SHALL 包含 header `x-agentcube-session-id: abc123`\n146: \n147: #### Scenario: 执行命令请求\n148: \n149: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command(\"ls -la\", timeout=30)`\n150: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n151: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}api/execute`\n152: - **AND** body 为 JSON `{\"command\": [\"ls\", \"-la\"], \"timeout\": \"30s\"}`\n153: - **AND** read timeout 为 `30 + 2.0 = 32.0` 秒（缓冲 2 秒避免 ReadTimeout）\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 字符串转数组\n156: \n157: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command(\"ls -la\")` (字符串参数)\n158: - **WHEN** 构造请求 body\n159: - **THEN** `command` SHALL 被转换为 `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 数组参数\n162: \n163: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command([\"ls\", \"-la\"])` (数组参数)\n164: - **WHEN** 构造请求 body\n165: - **THEN** `command` SHALL 直接使用 `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]`\n166: \n167: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 默认超时\n168: \n169: - **GIVEN** 调用 `execute_command(\"ls\")` 未指定 timeout\n170: - **AND** 客户端默认 `timeout=120`\n171: - **WHEN** 构造请求\n172: - **THEN** body 中 `timeout` SHALL 为 `\"120s\"`\n173: - **AND** read timeout SHALL 为 `120 + 2.0 = 122.0` 秒\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 非零退出码\n176: \n177: - **GIVEN** 远程命令返回 JSON `{\"exit_code\": 1, \"stderr\": \"error output\", \"stdout\": \"\"}`\n178: - **WHEN** 解析响应\n179: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `CommandExecutionError`，包含 `exit_code=1`, `stderr=\"error output\"`, `command`\n180: \n181: #### Scenario: 执行命令 - 成功\n182: \n183: - **GIVEN** 远程命令返回 JSON `{\"exit_code\": 0, \"stdout\": \"file1\\nfile2\", \"stderr\": \"\"}`\n184: - **WHEN** 解析响应\n185: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 返回 `\"file1\\nfile2\"`\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: 写文件请求\n188: \n189: - **GIVEN** 调用 `write_file(\"hello world\", \"/tmp/test.txt\")`\n190: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n191: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}api/files`\n192: - **AND** body 为 JSON `{\"path\": \"/tmp/test.txt\", \"content\": \"aGVsbG8gd29ybGQ=\" (base64), \"mode\": \"0644\"}`\n193: - **AND** header `Content-Type: application/json`\n194: \n195: #### Scenario: 写文件 - base64 编码\n196: \n197: - **GIVEN** `content` 为 UTF-8 字符串\n198: - **WHEN** 构造请求 body\n199: - **THEN** `content` SHALL 先编码为 UTF-8 字节，再 base64 编码为字符串\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: 上传文件请求\n202: \n203: - **GIVEN** 调用 `upload_file(\"/local/file.txt\", \"/remote/file.txt\")`\n204: - **AND** 本地文件存在\n205: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n206: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}api/files` (multipart/form-data)\n207: - **AND** 包含 `files={'file': <file content>}`\n208: - **AND** 包含 `data={'path': '/remote/file.txt', 'mode': '0644'}`\n209: - **AND** header 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id`\n210: - **AND** 不设置 JSON Content-Type（因为是 multipart）\n211: \n212: #### Scenario: 上传文件 - 文件不存在\n213: \n214: - **GIVEN** 本地文件 `/nonexistent/file.txt` 不存在\n215: - **WHEN** 调用 `upload_file(\"/nonexistent/file.txt\", \"/remote/file.txt\")`\n216: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `FileNotFoundError`\n217: \n218: #### Scenario: 下载文件请求\n219: \n220: - **GIVEN** 调用 `download_file(\"/remote/file.txt\", \"/local/file.txt\")`\n221: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n222: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `GET {base_url}api/files/remote/file.txt` (去除前导 `/`)\n223: - **AND** 设置 `stream=True`\n224: - **AND** 将响应内容写入本地路径 `/local/file.txt`\n225: \n226: #### Scenario: 下载文件 - 创建父目录\n227: \n228: - **GIVEN** 调用 `download_file(\"/remote/file.txt\", \"/local/subdir/file.txt\")`\n229: - **AND** `/local/subdir/` 目录不存在\n230: - **WHEN** 写入文件\n231: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 创建父目录 `/local/subdir/`\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: 列出文件请求\n234: \n235: - **GIVEN** 调用 `list_files(\"/home\")`\n236: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n237: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `GET {base_url}api/files` 并带上 query 参数 `path=/home`\n238: \n239: #### Scenario: 列出文件 - 默认路径\n240: \n241: - **GIVEN** 调用 `list_files()` 未传入参数\n242: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n243: - **THEN** query 参数 `path` SHALL 默认为 `\".\"`\n244: \n245: #### Scenario: Close 方法\n246: \n247: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 有活跃的 HTTP session\n248: - **WHEN** 调用 `client.close()`\n249: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 关闭底层的 `requests.Session`\n250: \n251: ---\n252: \n253: ### Requirement: Agent Runtime Data Plane HTTP 客户端\n254: \n255: 系统应实现 `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 支持通过 Router 调用 Agent Runtime。\n256: \n257: #### Scenario: Base URL 构建\n258: \n259: - **GIVEN** 构造时传入 `router_url=\"https://router.example.com\"`, `namespace=\"prod\"`, `agent_name=\"my-agent\"`\n260: - **WHEN** 初始化客户端\n261: - **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL 为 `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/prod/agent-runtimes/my-agent/invocations/\")`\n262: \n263: #### Scenario: Bootstrap Session ID - 成功\n264: \n265: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 初始化完成\n266: - **WHEN** 调用 `bootstrap_session_id()`\n267: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `GET {base_url}` (无额外路径)\n268: - **AND** 从响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 获取并返回 session id\n269: \n270: #### Scenario: Bootstrap Session ID - 缺失 header\n271: \n272: - **GIVEN** bootstrap `GET` 请求成功但响应 header 中没有 `x-agentcube-session-id`\n273: - **WHEN** 尝试提取 session id\n274: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `ValueError(\"Missing required response header: x-agentcube-session-id\")`\n275: \n276: #### Scenario: Invoke 请求\n277: \n278: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 为 `\"sess-123\"`\n279: - **WHEN** 调用 `invoke(session_id, {\"input\": \"test\"}, timeout=60)`\n280: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL `POST {base_url}`\n281: - **AND** headers 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-123`\n282: - **AND** headers 包含 `Content-Type: application/json`\n283: - **AND** body 为 JSON `{\"input\": \"test\"}`\n284: - **AND** 超时为 `(connect_timeout, 60)` 默认 `(5.0, 60)`\n285: \n286: #### Scenario: Invoke 无 session_id\n287: \n288: - **GIVEN** `session_id` 为 `None` 或空字符串\n289: - **WHEN** 调用 `invoke(session_id, payload)`\n290: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 抛出 `ValueError(\"AgentRuntime session_id is not initialized\")`\n291: \n292: #### Scenario: Invoke 返回 Response 对象\n293: \n294: - **GIVEN** `invoke` 请求成功\n295: - **WHEN** 函数返回\n296: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 返回 `requests.Response` 对象（由调用方解析 JSON）\n297: \n298: #### Scenario: Session Header 常量\n299: \n300: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 类定义\n301: - **WHEN** 检查类属性\n302: - **THEN** `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` SHALL 定义为类常量\n303: \n304: #### Scenario: Close 方法\n305: \n306: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 有活跃的 HTTP session\n307: - **WHEN** 调用 `client.close()`\n308: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 关闭底层的 `requests.Session`\n309: \n310: ---\n311: \n312: ### Requirement: 超时配置统一\n313: \n314: 系统应支持统一的超时配置，默认读超时 120 秒，连接超时 5 秒。\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: Control Plane 默认超时\n317: \n318: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` 使用默认参数构造\n319: - **WHEN** 发送任意请求\n320: - **THEN** 超时 SHALL 为 `(5.0, 120)` (connect_timeout, read_timeout)\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: Code Interpreter Data Plane 默认超时\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 使用默认参数构造\n325: - **WHEN** 发送任意请求\n326: - **THEN** 默认 `timeout` SHALL 为 `120`，`connect_timeout` SHALL 为 `5.0`\n327: \n328: #### Scenario: Agent Runtime Data Plane 默认超时\n329: \n330: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 使用默认参数构造\n331: - **WHEN** 发送任意请求\n332: - **THEN** 默认 `timeout` SHALL 为 `120`，`connect_timeout` SHALL 为 `5.0`\n333: \n334: #### Scenario: 自定义超时\n335: \n336: - **GIVEN** 构造 `ControlPlaneClient(timeout=60, connect_timeout=3.0)`\n337: - **WHEN** 发送请求\n338: - **THEN** 超时 SHALL 为 `(3.0, 60)`\n339: \n340: #### Scenario: Per-call 超时覆盖 - execute_command\n341: \n342: - **GIVEN** `execute_command(command, timeout=30)`\n343: - **WHEN** 该调用执行\n344: - **THEN** read timeout SHALL 使用 `30`（加缓冲 2 秒后为 32），connect timeout 使用实例默认值\n345: \n346: #### Scenario: Per-call 超时覆盖 - invoke\n347: \n348: - **GIVEN** `invoke(..., timeout=30.0)`\n349: - **WHEN** 该调用执行\n350: - **THEN** read timeout SHALL 使用 `30.0`，connect timeout 使用实例默认值\n351: \n352: ---\n353: \n354: ### Requirement: 异常层次结构\n355: \n356: 系统应定义清晰的异常类层次，便于调用方捕获和处理错误。\n357: \n358: #### Scenario: 异常继承\n359: \n360: - **GIVEN** 异常类定义在 `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n361: - **WHEN** 检查类层次\n362: - **THEN** `AgentCubeError` SHALL 继承 `Exception`\n363: - **AND** `CommandExecutionError` SHALL 继承 `AgentCubeError`\n364: - **AND** `SessionError` SHALL 继承 `AgentCubeError`\n365: - **AND** `DataPlaneError` SHALL 继承 `AgentCubeError`\n366: \n367: #### Scenario: CommandExecutionError 构造\n368: \n369: - **GIVEN** 远程命令执行失败，退出码为 2，stderr 为 \"failed\"，命令为 \"ls -la\"\n370: - **WHEN** 构造 `CommandExecutionError(2, \"failed\", \"ls -la\")`\n371: - **THEN** 异常 SHALL 包含属性 `exit_code=2`, `stderr=\"failed\"`, `command=\"ls -la\"`\n372: - **AND** 异常消息 SHALL 为 `\"Command failed (exit 2): failed\"`\n373: \n374: #### Scenario: CommandExecutionError 默认 command\n375: \n376: - **GIVEN** 构造 `CommandExecutionError(1, \"error\")` 不传入 command\n377: - **WHEN** 异常创建\n378: - **THEN** `command` 属性 SHALL 为 `None`\n379: \n380: #### Scenario: SessionError 基类\n381: \n382: - **GIVEN** `SessionError` 定义\n383: - **WHEN** 检查类定义\n384: - **THEN** `SessionError` SHALL 为 `AgentCubeError` 的子类，文档字符串为 \"Raised when session creation or management fails\"\n385: \n386: #### Scenario: DataPlaneError 基类\n387: \n388: - **GIVEN** `DataPlaneError` 定义\n389: - **WHEN** 检查类定义\n390: - **THEN** `DataPlaneError` SHALL 为 `AgentCubeError` 的子类，文档字符串为 \"Raised when Data Plane operations fail\"\n391: \n392: ---\n393: \n394: ### Requirement: Token 文件读取\n395: \n396: 系统应支持从文件读取认证 token，处理文件不存在情况。\n397: \n398: #### Scenario: 读取 token 文件成功\n399: \n400: - **GIVEN** 文件 `/path/to/token` 内容为 `\"my-secret-token\\n\"`\n401: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file(\"/path/to/token\")`\n402: - **THEN** 返回 `\"my-secret-token\"` (已 strip)\n403: \n404: #### Scenario: 读取 token 文件 - 多行\n405: \n406: - **GIVEN** 文件内容为 `\"token-line1\\ntoken-line2\\n\"`\n407: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file`\n408: - **THEN** 返回 `\"token-line1\\ntoken-line2\"` (仅 strip 前后空白)\n409: \n410: #### Scenario: 文件不存在\n411: \n412: - **GIVEN** 文件 `/nonexistent/token` 不存在\n413: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file(\"/nonexistent/token\")`\n414: - **THEN** 返回空字符串 `\"\"` (不抛出异常)\n415: \n416: #### Scenario: 文件读取权限错误\n417: \n418: - **GIVEN** 文件存在但无读取权限\n419: - **WHEN** 调用 `read_token_from_file`\n420: - **THEN** 异常 SHALL 向上传播（不捕获）\n421: \n422: ---\n423: \n424: ### Requirement: 日志工具\n425: \n426: 系统应提供日志工具函数。\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: Logger 创建\n429: \n430: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\")`\n431: - **WHEN** 函数返回\n432: - **THEN** 返回一个 `logging.Logger` 实例，名称为 `\"agentcube.client\"`\n433: \n434: #### Scenario: 默认日志级别\n435: \n436: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\")` 不传入 level\n437: - **WHEN** 创建 logger\n438: - **THEN** 日志级别 SHALL 默认为 `logging.INFO`\n439: \n440: #### Scenario: 自定义日志级别\n441: \n442: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\", level=logging.DEBUG)`\n443: - **WHEN** 创建 logger\n444: - **THEN** 日志级别 SHALL 为 `logging.DEBUG`\n445: \n446: #### Scenario: 字符串日志级别\n447: \n448: - **GIVEN** 调用 `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\", level=\"DEBUG\")`\n449: - **WHEN** 创建 logger\n450: - **THEN** 系统 SHALL 将字符串 `\"DEBUG\"` 转换为 `logging.DEBUG`\n451: \n452: ---\n453: \n454: ### Requirement: 公共 API 导出\n455: \n456: 系统应从包根导出公共类。\n457: \n458: #### Scenario: 根包导出\n459: \n460: - **GIVEN** `from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient`\n461: - **WHEN** 执行导入\n462: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterClient` 和 `AgentRuntimeClient` SHALL 可用\n463: \n464: #### Scenario: clients 子包导出\n465: \n466: - **GIVEN** `from agentcube.clients import ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n467: - **WHEN** 执行导入\n468: - **THEN** 三个类 SHALL 可用\n469: \n470: #### Scenario: __all__ 定义\n471: \n472: - **GIVEN** `agentcube/__init__.py` 文件\n473: - **WHEN** 检查 `__all__`\n474: - **THEN** `__all__` SHALL 包含 `[\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]`\n475: \n476: #### Scenario: clients __all__ 定义\n477: \n478: - **GIVEN** `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` 文件\n479: - **WHEN** 检查 `__all__`\n480: - **THEN** `__all__` SHALL 包含 `[\"ControlPlaneClient\", \"CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\", \"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\"]`\n481: \n482: ---\n483: \n484: ## Implementation Files\n485: \n486: | File | Purpose |\n487: |------|---------|\n488: | `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` 函数 |\n489: | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` 函数 |\n490: | `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` 函数 |\n491: | `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | 工具模块标记 |\n492: | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | 异常类定义 |\n493: | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` 类 |\n494: | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 类 |\n495: | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` 类 |\n496: | `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | 客户端导出 |\n497: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | 包根导出 |\n498: \n499: ---\n500: \n501: ## Dependencies\n502: \n503: | Package | Purpose |\n504: |---------|---------|\n505: | `requests` | HTTP 客户端 |\n506: | `PyJWT>=2.0.0` | JWT 处理（如需要） |\n507: | `cryptography` | 加密支持（如需要） |\n508: \n509: ---\n510: \n511: ## Validation Checklist\n512: \n513: - [ ] `create_session()` 创建带 `HTTPAdapter` 的 `requests.Session`\n514: - [ ] `create_session()` 支持自定义 `pool_connections` 和 `pool_maxsize`\n515: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.create_session` POST 正确 JSON body 并返回 `sessionId`\n516: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session` 对 404 返回 `True`\n517: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient` 从 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 读取 base_url\n518: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient` 从参数或文件读取 auth_token\n519: - [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.close()` 关闭 session\n520: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 正确构建 base_url\n521: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` 设置 `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n522: - [ ] `execute_command` 正确构造请求 body 和超时\n523: - [ ] `execute_command` 对非零退出码抛出 `CommandExecutionError`\n524: - [ ] `write_file` base64 编码 content\n525: - [ ] `upload_file` 使用 multipart/form-data\n526: - [ ] `download_file` 使用 `stream=True`\n527: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id` 提取 header\n528: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke` 正确设置 headers\n529: - [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER` 常量\n530: - [ ] 超时默认值 `(connect_timeout=5.0, timeout=120)`\n531: - [ ] 异常类层次正确\n532: - [ ] `CommandExecutionError` 包含 `exit_code`, `stderr`, `command`\n533: - [ ] `read_token_from_file` 对不存在文件返回空字符串\n534: - [ ] `get_logger` 返回正确命名的 logger\n535: - [ ] 公共 API 从 `agentcube` 和 `agentcube.clients` 正确导出\n\n(End of file - total 535 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Specification: AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube Python SDK 实现统一的 HTTP 客户端基础设施，支持控制面和数据面的 HTTP 通信，包括连接池管理、超时配置、会话管理和错误处理。\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: HTTP Session 创建与连接池\n\n系统应使用 `requests.Session` 配合 `HTTPAdapter` 实现连接池复用，支持自定义连接池大小。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775882667315,"end":1775882667337}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882667343,"sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","part":{"id":"prt_d7adb01d0001jkF1PNpqEl8eci","messageID":"msg_d7adae6ab001LwaaubpTbs2w1t","sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-f82db590c469415ab1393549e95c2f75","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube Python SDK Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Python client library (`agentcube-sdk`) for creating Code Interpreter sessions via the Workload Manager (control plane) and executing code/files via the Router (data plane), plus invoking AgentRuntime workloads through the Router.\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: `CodeInterpreterClient` lifecycle\n10: The system SHALL construct a client that either reuses `session_id` or creates a session via `ControlPlaneClient.create_session`, then initializes `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` with header `x-agentcube-session-id`.\n11: \n12: #### Scenario: Context manager cleanup\n13: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterClient` is used as a context manager\n14: - **WHEN** the block exits (with or without exception)\n15: - **THEN** `__exit__` SHALL call `stop()`, which closes the data-plane session, deletes the control-plane session if `session_id` was set, and closes the control plane HTTP session\n16: \n17: #### Scenario: Data plane init failure after session create\n18: - **GIVEN** `session_id` was not provided and `create_session` succeeded\n19: - **WHEN** `_init_data_plane()` raises\n20: - **THEN** the client SHALL log a warning, call `delete_session(session_id)`, set `session_id` to `None`, and re-raise\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: Router URL required\n23: - **GIVEN** neither `router_url` nor environment variable `ROUTER_URL` is set\n24: - **WHEN** `CodeInterpreterClient.__init__` runs\n25: - **THEN** it SHALL raise `ValueError` explaining that Router URL must be provided via argument or `ROUTER_URL`\n26: \n27: ### Requirement: Code Interpreter — execute, files, stop\n28: The system SHALL expose `execute_command`, `run_code`, `write_file`, `upload_file`, `download_file`, `list_files`, and `stop` delegating to the data plane client where applicable.\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: Command non-zero exit\n31: - **GIVEN** `execute_command` receives a response with `exit_code != 0`\n32: - **WHEN** the response JSON is parsed\n33: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `CommandExecutionError` with `exit_code`, `stderr`, and `command`\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Python code execution path\n36: - **GIVEN** `language` is `python`, `py`, or `python3`\n37: - **WHEN** `run_code` runs\n38: - **THEN** the system SHALL write a timestamped `.py` file via `write_file` and execute `python3 <file>` through `execute_command`\n39: \n40: ### Requirement: `AgentRuntimeClient` lifecycle\n41: The system SHALL bootstrap or reuse `session_id` from the Agent Runtime invocation endpoint via `GET` on the base invocation URL, then `POST` JSON payloads with session header.\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: Context manager\n44: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeClient` is used as a context manager\n45: - **WHEN** the block exits\n46: - **THEN** `close()` SHALL close the underlying `requests.Session`\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: Bootstrap session id\n49: - **GIVEN** `session_id` is not provided\n50: - **WHEN** the client initializes\n51: - **THEN** it SHALL `GET` `{router}/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/` and read header `x-agentcube-session-id`; if missing, raise `ValueError` with message `Missing required response header: x-agentcube-session-id`\n52: \n53: #### Scenario: Invoke without session\n54: - **GIVEN** `session_id` is falsy\n55: - **WHEN** `invoke` is called\n56: - **THEN** it SHALL raise `ValueError(\"AgentRuntime session_id is not initialized\")`\n57: \n58: ### Requirement: HTTP client contracts — control plane\n59: The system SHALL use `requests.Session` with connection pooling (`HTTPAdapter`) for Workload Manager calls.\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: Create session\n62: - **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient.create_session(name, namespace, metadata=None, ttl=3600)`\n63: - **WHEN** the request succeeds\n64: - **THEN** the client SHALL `POST {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` with JSON body `{\"name\",\"namespace\",\"ttl\",\"metadata\"}` and return `data[\"sessionId\"]` or raise `ValueError` if absent\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Delete session\n67: - **GIVEN** `delete_session(session_id)`\n68: - **WHEN** the server returns 404\n69: - **THEN** the method SHALL return `True`; on other failures it SHALL log and return `False`\n70: \n71: #### Scenario: Workload Manager URL and auth\n72: - **GIVEN** `workload_manager_url` and `auth_token` may be omitted\n73: - **WHEN** the client initializes\n74: - **THEN** `base_url` SHALL resolve from `workload_manager_url` or `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`; token SHALL resolve from `auth_token` or `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` via `read_token_from_file`, and if present set `Authorization: Bearer {token}`\n75: \n76: ### Requirement: HTTP client contracts — data plane (Code Interpreter)\n77: The system SHALL target Router-relative paths under `{base_url}` derived from `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/{ns}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/\")` unless `base_url` is passed explicitly.\n78: \n79: #### Scenario: Execute command\n80: - **WHEN** `execute_command` posts to `api/execute`\n81: - **THEN** the body SHALL be JSON `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}` and read timeout SHALL be `timeout_value + 2.0` seconds when numeric (to avoid `ReadTimeout` before PicoD returns exit 124)\n82: \n83: #### Scenario: Files API\n84: - **WHEN** `write_file` runs\n85: - **THEN** it SHALL `POST api/files` with base64 `content`, `path`, `mode` `\"0644\"`\n86: - **WHEN** `upload_file` runs\n87: - **THEN** it SHALL `POST` multipart to `api/files` with headers including `x-agentcube-session-id`\n88: \n89: ### Requirement: HTTP client contracts — data plane (Agent Runtime)\n90: The system SHALL `POST` JSON to the invocation base URL with headers `x-agentcube-session-id` and `Content-Type: application/json`.\n91: \n92: #### Scenario: Invoke timeout tuple\n93: - **GIVEN** `invoke(..., timeout=None)`\n94: - **WHEN** the request is sent\n95: - **THEN** `timeout` SHALL be `(connect_timeout, self.timeout)` where `self.timeout` defaults to `120`\n96: \n97: ### Requirement: Session header management\n98: The system SHALL use lowercase header name `x-agentcube-session-id` for SDK Router requests (`CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` default session header; `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` uses class constant `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"`).\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: Code Interpreter session header\n101: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` is constructed\n102: - **WHEN** any `_request` or upload runs\n103: - **THEN** the session SHALL include `x-agentcube-session-id: {session_id}` (upload sets it explicitly on the multipart POST)\n104: \n105: ### Requirement: Exception hierarchy\n106: The system SHALL define `AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError`, `SessionError`, and `DataPlaneError` in `agentcube.exceptions`.\n107: \n108: #### Scenario: Command failure\n109: - **GIVEN** remote command returns non-zero exit code in JSON\n110: - **WHEN** `execute_command` processes the response\n111: - **THEN** it SHALL raise `CommandExecutionError` (subclass of `AgentCubeError`)\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: SessionError / DataPlaneError usage\n114: - **GIVEN** the current package sources under `agentcube/`\n115: - **WHEN** searching for `raise SessionError` / `raise DataPlaneError`\n116: - **THEN** these classes are defined for extension but not raised by the core client modules in the extracted tree (callers MAY rely on `ValueError`, `requests` exceptions, or `CommandExecutionError`)\n117: \n118: ### Requirement: Timeout behavior\n119: The system SHALL default control-plane and data-plane read timeouts to `120` seconds and connect timeout to `5.0` seconds unless overridden per call.\n120: \n121: #### Scenario: Per-call override for code execution\n122: - **GIVEN** `execute_command(command, timeout=None)`\n123: - **WHEN** `timeout` is `None`\n124: - **THEN** the effective timeout value SHALL default to `self.timeout` (`120`) for constructing the PicoD timeout string and read-timeout buffer logic\n125: \n126: #### Scenario: AgentRuntimeClient constructor timeouts\n127: - **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeClient(..., timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0)`\n128: - **WHEN** `invoke` is called without `timeout`\n129: - **THEN** read timeout SHALL be `120` (instance default)\n130: \n131: ---\n132: \n133: **Public package surface:** `agentcube/__init__.py` exports only `CodeInterpreterClient` and `AgentRuntimeClient` in `__all__`.\n\n(End of file - total 133 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube Python SDK Specification\n\n## Purpose\n\nPython client library (`agentcube-sdk`) for creating Code Interpreter sessions via the Workload Manager (control plane) and executing code/files via the Router (data plane), plus invoking AgentRuntime workloads through the Router.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: `CodeInterpreterClient` lifecycle\nThe system SHALL construct a client that either reuses `session_id` or creates a session via `ControlPlaneClient.create_session`, then initializes `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` with header `x-agentcube-session-id`.\n\n#### Scenario: Context manager cleanup\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterClient` is used as a context manager\n- **WHEN** the block exits (with or without exception)\n- **THEN** `__exit__` SHALL call `stop()`, which closes the data-plane session, deletes the control-plane session if `session_id` was set, and closes the control plane HTTP session\n\n#### Scenario: Data plane init failure after session create\n- **GIVEN** `session_id` was not provided and `create_session` succeeded\n- **WHEN** `_init_data_plane()` raises\n- **THEN** the client SHALL log a warning, call `delete_session(session_id)`, set `session_id` to `None`, and re-raise","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/spec.md","time":{"start":1775882667319,"end":1775882667342}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882667345,"sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","part":{"id":"prt_d7adb0513001lZ0ordSQNVUICC","messageID":"msg_d7adae6ab001LwaaubpTbs2w1t","sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b1453fa5cafc42198d78a31e431d8f62","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube Python SDK — Design\n2: \n3: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/`.\n4: \n5: ## Package layout\n6: \n7: | Path | Role |\n8: |------|------|\n9: | `pyproject.toml` | Package `agentcube-sdk`, dependencies |\n10: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Public exports |\n11: | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient` |\n12: | `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | `AgentRuntimeClient` |\n13: | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Exception classes |\n14: | `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | Re-exports client classes |\n15: | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` |\n16: | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` |\n17: | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` |\n18: | `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` |\n19: | `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` |\n20: | `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` |\n21: | `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | Empty (module marker) |\n22: | `examples/basic_usage.py`, `examples/agent_runtime_usage.py`, `scripts/e2e_picod_test.py`, `tests/*.py` | Non-library artifacts |\n23: \n24: ## Public exports (`agentcube/__init__.py`)\n25: \n26: ```python\n27: from .code_interpreter import CodeInterpreterClient\n28: from .agent_runtime import AgentRuntimeClient\n29: \n30: __all__ = [\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]\n31: ```\n32: \n33: `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` additionally exports (not in root `__all__`):\n34: \n35: ```python\n36: __all__ = [\n37:     \"ControlPlaneClient\",\n38:     \"CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\",\n39:     \"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\",\n40: ]\n41: ```\n42: \n43: ## Configuration (no single `Configuration` class)\n44: \n45: There is **no** dedicated configuration dataclass. Defaults and environment resolution are distributed across:\n46: \n47: | Component | Resolved settings |\n48: |-----------|-------------------|\n49: | `ControlPlaneClient` | `base_url` ← `workload_manager_url` or `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`; `Authorization` ← `auth_token` or SA token file; `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10` |\n50: | `CodeInterpreterClient` | `router_url` ← arg or `ROUTER_URL` (required); `workload_manager_url` / `auth_token` passed to `ControlPlaneClient`; `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `verbose`, `session_id` |\n51: | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` | `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`; `base_url` from `base_url` **or** `router_url`+`namespace`+`cr_name` |\n52: | `AgentRuntimeClient` | `router_url` ← arg or `ROUTER_URL`; `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0` passed to data plane |\n53: | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` | same timeout defaults as above |\n54: \n55: ## `CodeInterpreterClient` (`agentcube/code_interpreter.py`)\n56: \n57: ```python\n58: class CodeInterpreterClient:\n59:     def __init__(\n60:         self,\n61:         name: str = \"my-interpreter\",\n62:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n63:         ttl: int = 3600,\n64:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n65:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n66:         auth_token: Optional[str] = None,\n67:         verbose: bool = False,\n68:         session_id: Optional[str] = None,\n69:     ): ...\n70: \n71:     def _init_data_plane(self) -> None: ...\n72: \n73:     def __enter__(self): ...\n74:     def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb) -> None: ...\n75: \n76:     def stop(self) -> None: ...\n77: \n78:     def execute_command(self, command: str, timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> str: ...\n79:     def run_code(self, language: str, code: str, timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> str: ...\n80:     def write_file(self, content: str, remote_path: str) -> None: ...\n81:     def upload_file(self, local_path: str, remote_path: str) -> None: ...\n82:     def download_file(self, remote_path: str, local_path: str) -> None: ...\n83:     def list_files(self, path: str = \".\"): ...\n84: ```\n85: \n86: **Fields set on instance:** `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `verbose`, `logger`, `cp_client`, `router_url`, `session_id`, `dp_client`.\n87: \n88: ## `AgentRuntimeClient` (`agentcube/agent_runtime.py`)\n89: \n90: ```python\n91: class AgentRuntimeClient:\n92:     def __init__(\n93:         self,\n94:         agent_name: str,\n95:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n96:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n97:         verbose: bool = False,\n98:         session_id: Optional[str] = None,\n99:         timeout: int = 120,\n100:         connect_timeout: float = 5.0,\n101:     ): ...\n102: \n103:     def __enter__(self): ...\n104:     def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb) -> None: ...\n105: \n106:     def invoke(self, payload: Dict[str, Any], timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> Any: ...\n107: \n108:     def close(self) -> None: ...\n109: ```\n110: \n111: **Fields:** `agent_name`, `namespace`, `timeout`, `connect_timeout`, `logger`, `router_url`, `session_id`, `dp_client`.\n112: \n113: ## `ControlPlaneClient` (`agentcube/clients/control_plane.py`)\n114: \n115: ```python\n116: class ControlPlaneClient:\n117:     def __init__(\n118:         self,\n119:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n120:         auth_token: Optional[str] = None,\n121:         timeout: int = 120,\n122:         connect_timeout: float = 5.0,\n123:         pool_connections: int = 10,\n124:         pool_maxsize: int = 10,\n125:     ): ...\n126: \n127:     def create_session(\n128:         self,\n129:         name: str = \"my-interpreter\",\n130:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n131:         metadata: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None,\n132:         ttl: int = 3600,\n133:     ) -> str: ...\n134: \n135:     def delete_session(self, session_id: str) -> bool: ...\n136: \n137:     def close(self) -> None: ...\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ### Control plane — HTTP\n141: \n142: | Method | Path | Notes |\n143: |--------|------|-------|\n144: | `POST` | `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` | JSON body: `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `metadata` |\n145: | `DELETE` | `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}` | 404 treated as success in `delete_session` |\n146: \n147: **Headers (default on `self.session`):**\n148: \n149: - `Content-Type`: `application/json`\n150: - `Authorization`: `Bearer {token}` if token non-empty\n151: \n152: **Timeout:** `(connect_timeout, timeout)` on each request.\n153: \n154: ## `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` (`agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py`)\n155: \n156: ```python\n157: class CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient:\n158:     def __init__(\n159:         self,\n160:         session_id: str,\n161:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n162:         namespace: Optional[str] = None,\n163:         cr_name: Optional[str] = None,\n164:         base_url: Optional[str] = None,\n165:         timeout: int = 120,\n166:         connect_timeout: float = 5.0,\n167:         pool_connections: int = 10,\n168:         pool_maxsize: int = 10,\n169:     ): ...\n170: \n171:     def _request(self, method: str, endpoint: str, body: Optional[bytes] = None, **kwargs) -> requests.Response: ...\n172: \n173:     def execute_command(self, command: Union[str, List[str]], timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> str: ...\n174:     def run_code(self, language: str, code: str, timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> str: ...\n175:     def write_file(self, content: str, remote_path: str) -> None: ...\n176:     def upload_file(self, local_path: str, remote_path: str) -> None: ...\n177:     def download_file(self, remote_path: str, local_path: str) -> None: ...\n178:     def list_files(self, path: str = \".\") -> Any: ...\n179:     def close(self) -> None: ...\n180: ```\n181: \n182: ### Data plane (Code Interpreter) — base URL\n183: \n184: If `base_url` is not provided:\n185: \n186: ```text\n187: base_path = \"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/\"\n188: self.base_url = urljoin(router_url, base_path)\n189: ```\n190: \n191: ### Data plane — HTTP (relative to `self.base_url`)\n192: \n193: | Method | Relative path | Body / params |\n194: |--------|---------------|---------------|\n195: | `POST` | `api/execute` | JSON `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}` |\n196: | `POST` | `api/files` | JSON `{\"path\", \"content\" (base64), \"mode\": \"0644\"}` |\n197: | `POST` | `api/files` (multipart) | `files={'file': ...}`, `data={'path', 'mode'}` |\n198: | `GET` | `api/files/{clean_path}` | `stream=True` for download (`clean_path = remote_path.lstrip(\"/\")`) |\n199: | `GET` | `api/files` | query `path` |\n200: \n201: **Headers:**\n202: \n203: - Default session header: `x-agentcube-session-id: {session_id}`\n204: - JSON requests: `Content-Type: application/json` when `body` is set in `_request`\n205: - Multipart upload: `x-agentcube-session-id` only (no JSON Content-Type on the outer request)\n206: \n207: **Note:** Docstring states Router handles JWT; SDK does not set `Authorization` on data plane.\n208: \n209: ## `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` (`agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`)\n210: \n211: ```python\n212: class AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient:\n213:     SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"\n214: \n215:     def __init__(\n216:         self,\n217:         router_url: str,\n218:         namespace: str,\n219:         agent_name: str,\n220:         timeout: int = 120,\n221:         connect_timeout: float = 5.0,\n222:         pool_connections: int = 10,\n223:         pool_maxsize: int = 10,\n224:     ): ...\n225: \n226:     def bootstrap_session_id(self) -> str: ...\n227: \n228:     def invoke(\n229:         self,\n230:         session_id: str,\n231:         payload: Dict[str, Any],\n232:         timeout: Optional[float] = None,\n233:     ) -> requests.Response: ...\n234: \n235:     def close(self) -> None: ...\n236: ```\n237: \n238: ### Data plane (Agent Runtime) — base URL\n239: \n240: ```text\n241: base_path = f\"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/\"\n242: self.base_url = urljoin(router_url, base_path)\n243: ```\n244: \n245: ### Data plane — HTTP\n246: \n247: | Method | URL | Headers | Body |\n248: |--------|-----|---------|------|\n249: | `GET` | `self.base_url` | (session default headers only) | — |\n250: | `POST` | `self.base_url` | `x-agentcube-session-id`, `Content-Type: application/json` | `json=payload` |\n251: \n252: **Timeouts:** `(connect_timeout, timeout)` where `timeout` for `invoke` read side is the method argument or `self.timeout`.\n253: \n254: ## `create_session` (`agentcube/utils/http.py`)\n255: \n256: ```python\n257: def create_session(\n258:     pool_connections: int = 10,\n259:     pool_maxsize: int = 10,\n260: ) -> requests.Session: ...\n261: ```\n262: \n263: Mounts `HTTPAdapter` for `http://` and `https://`.\n264: \n265: ## `read_token_from_file` (`agentcube/utils/utils.py`)\n266: \n267: ```python\n268: def read_token_from_file(file_path: str) -> str: ...\n269: ```\n270: \n271: Returns file contents stripped, or `\"\"` on `FileNotFoundError`.\n272: \n273: ## `get_logger` (`agentcube/utils/log.py`)\n274: \n275: ```python\n276: def get_logger(name: str, level: Union[int, str] = logging.INFO) -> logging.Logger: ...\n277: ```\n278: \n279: ## Exception hierarchy (`agentcube/exceptions.py`)\n280: \n281: ```python\n282: class AgentCubeError(Exception):\n283:     \"\"\"Base exception for AgentCube SDK\"\"\"\n284:     pass\n285: \n286: class CommandExecutionError(AgentCubeError):\n287:     def __init__(self, exit_code, stderr, command=None):\n288:         self.exit_code = exit_code\n289:         self.stderr = stderr\n290:         self.command = command\n291:         super().__init__(f\"Command failed (exit {exit_code}): {stderr}\")\n292: \n293: class SessionError(AgentCubeError):\n294:     \"\"\"Raised when session creation or management fails\"\"\"\n295:     pass\n296: \n297: class DataPlaneError(AgentCubeError):\n298:     \"\"\"Raised when Data Plane operations fail\"\"\"\n299:     pass\n300: ```\n301: \n302: ## Dependencies (`sdk-python/pyproject.toml`)\n303: \n304: ```toml\n305: dependencies = [\n306:     \"requests\",\n307:     \"PyJWT>=2.0.0\",\n308:     \"cryptography\",\n309: ]\n310: ```\n311: \n312: - `requires-python = \">=3.10\"`\n313: - Build: `setuptools>=61.0`, `wheel`; backend `setuptools.build_meta`\n314: - Packages: `where = [\".\"]`, `include = [\"agentcube*\"]`, `namespaces = false`\n\n(End of file - total 314 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube Python SDK — Design\n\nSource root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/sdk-python/`.\n\n## Package layout\n\n| Path | Role |\n|------|------|\n| `pyproject.toml` | Package `agentcube-sdk`, dependencies |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | Public exports |\n| `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient` |\n| `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | `AgentRuntimeClient` |\n| `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Exception classes |\n| `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | Re-exports client classes |\n| `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` |\n| `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` |\n| `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/python-sdk/design.md","time":{"start":1775882667321,"end":1775882667343}}}}
