{"type":"text","timestamp":1775883166133,"sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae27ade001htRrHQKH03kpDe","messageID":"msg_d7ae238d80012B5Kw0WPqsNDZz","sessionID":"ses_285256028ffeeh5BnkvQQdRm31","type":"text","text":"**AR-029 Implementation Complete**\n\n## Summary\n\nAll code for the SDK HTTP 底层客户端 is implemented and tested.\n\n### Implementation Files:\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` - HTTP connection pooling |\n| `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` - Kubernetes SA token |\n| `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` - Logging utilities |\n| `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Exception hierarchy |\n| `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` - Workload Manager |\n| `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` |\n| `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient` - High-level client |\n| `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | `AgentRuntimeClient` - High-level client |\n\n### Test Coverage: **120 tests, 97% coverage**\n\n### Key Features Implemented:\n- HTTP session with HTTPAdapter connection pooling\n- Unified timeout config (connect=5.0s, read=120s)\n- Token reading from `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`\n- Exception hierarchy: `AgentCubeError → CommandExecutionError/SessionError/DataPlaneError`\n- Control plane: POST/DELETE for session management\n- Data plane: execute_command, file operations (write/upload/download/list)\n- Agent runtime: bootstrap_session_id, invoke with session header\n- Context manager lifecycle management","time":{"start":1775883166130,"end":1775883166130}}}
